{
  "name": "Expert Monk",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/magic/earth/strike-fist-stone-light.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You gain the following benefits for your Monk Class Features.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Monk Training</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Iron Palm:</strong> Choose an additional Melee Weapon Style. When you make an Attack with an Unarmed Strike, you can use both Weapon Enhancements.</p><p><strong>Step of the Wind:</strong> You gain an additional +1 Speed and Jump Distance.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Monk Stances</span></strong></span></p><p>You learn 1 additional Monk Stance.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spiritual Balance</span></strong></span></p><p>Your Ki Point maximum increases by 1. Whenever you regain Ki Points, you regain half of your maximum Ki instead.</p>",
